<![CDATA[
<ol>
<li>Chrome/Safari Only</li>
<li>Make browser window to about 300px width
<li>Now drag the border between 2nd column and 3rd column to right to exceed the browser window right border</li>
<li>Shall see the horizontal scrollbar appear</li>
<li>Maximize the browser window. Horizontal scrollbar disappear now. Remember the current thumb handle size of the scrollbar.</li>
<li>Restore the browser window. Horizontal scrollbar reappear.</li>
<li>The size of the thumb handle of the scrollbar shall be the same as it was</li>
<li>Drag the scrollbar thumb handle to the right, the column header and contents shall align well</li>
<li>done</li>
</ol>
]]>
